# Logs
# Anchored: an unanchored `logs` also matches src/pages/logs/, the Logs page's
# CSS parts, so a new part file there would be ignored without a word.
/logs/
*.log
npm-debug.log*
yarn-debug.log*
yarn-error.log*
pnpm-debug.log*
lerna-debug.log*

node_modules
dist
dist-ssr
*.local

